CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Aeglea BioTherapeutics Inc is a clinical-stage biotechnology company. It designs and develops innovative human enzyme therapeutics for patients with rare genetic diseases and cancer. The company's lead product candidate includes pegzilarginase, a recombinant human Arginase 1 enzyme, which is in an early clinical development stage.
